---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Case Study: Hospital BP Digital Transformation | Diogo Soares">
  <article class="py-16">
    <div class="section-container">
      
      {/* Header */}
      <header class="mb-12 max-w-3xl">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <a href="/" class="text-text-muted hover:text-accent transition-colors text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/><path d="M19 12H5"/></svg>
            <span>Back</span>
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-6">
          <span class="badge">Project Management</span>
          <span class="badge">Digital Transformation</span>
          <span class="badge">Healthcare</span>
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display text-text mb-6 leading-tight">
          Digital Transformation at Hospital BeneficÃªncia Portuguesa (BP)
        </h1>
        
        <p class="text-xl text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Complete redesign of patient journeys, integrating technology, data, and a patient-centric vision.
        </p>
      </header>

      {/* Hero Image / Overview Section */}
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-text mb-6">Overview</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-3xl">
          During my time as <strong class="text-text">Senior Project Manager</strong> at Weber Shandwick, I led the modernization of the digital ecosystem for Hospital BP, one of the largest medical-hospital centers in Latin America. The project consisted of a complete redesign of service journeys, integrating technology, data, and a patient-centric vision.
        </p>
      </section>

      {/* The Challenge */}
      <section class="mb-16">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-text mb-6">The Challenge: The Complexity of Digital Health</h2>
            <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">
              The healthcare sector presents unique criticality. The challenge was not just technical, but one of governance and compliance, operating in a high-complexity environment that required alignment among various decision-makers:
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-text-secondary">
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="text-accent font-bold">01.</span>
                <span><strong class="text-text">Critical Areas:</strong> Legal, Compliance, and Data Governance.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="text-accent font-bold">02.</span>
                <span><strong class="text-text">Medical Staff:</strong> Doctors and specialists with rigorous technical requirements.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="text-accent font-bold">03.</span>
                <span><strong class="text-text">Legacy Systems:</strong> Integration with existing scheduling and medical record databases.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-card border border-border">
            <img src="/images/hospital-bp-desafio.png" alt="BP Digital Challenge" class="w-full" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* Strategic Actions */}
      <section class="mb-16 bg-surface-subtle p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl border border-border">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-text mb-8">My Strategic Role</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div>
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-accent">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-display text-text mb-3">Product Vision & MVP</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
              We prioritized the redesign of high-impact journeys, such as digital scheduling, ensuring fast functional delivery to validate adoption before expansion.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-accent">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-display text-text mb-3">Multidisciplinary Leadership</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
              I coordinated Design, Development, Content, and Data teams, acting as the interface between technical teams and business stakeholders.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-accent">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2v4"/><path d="m16.2 4.2 2.8 2.8"/><path d="M18 12h4"/><path d="m16.2 19.8 2.8-2.8"/><path d="M12 18v4"/><path d="m4.2 19.8 2.8-2.8"/><path d="M2 12h4"/><path d="m4.2 4.2 2.8 2.8"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-display text-text mb-3">Agile Methodologies</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
              We used prioritization rituals and feedback cycles to adapt the roadmap as technical integration barriers were identified.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* Delivery Pillars Section with provided image */}
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-text mb-6">Delivery Pillars (Business & UX)</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-3xl">
          I utilized a set of strategic tools to ensure operational efficiency: Business Model Canvas, Design Thinking & UX, and a Data-Driven culture focused on continuous monitoring.
        </p>
        <div class="mb-12 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-card border border-border">
          <img src="/images/hospital-bp-resultados.png" alt="Methodology and Results" class="w-full" />
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* Impact Section */}
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-text mb-8">Impact Results</h2>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
          <div class="p-6 bg-surface-elevated rounded-2xl border border-border">
            <h4 class="text-accent font-bold mb-2">SEO & Organic</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">Information architecture optimization, raising rankings for critical search terms.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 bg-surface-elevated rounded-2xl border border-border">
            <h4 class="text-accent font-bold mb-2">Media Efficiency</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">Significant reduction in CAC due to higher relevance and better conversion journeys.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 bg-surface-elevated rounded-2xl border border-border">
            <h4 class="text-accent font-bold mb-2">100% Digital Scheduling</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">Modernization of the primary touchpoint between patient and institution.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 bg-surface-elevated rounded-2xl border border-border">
            <h4 class="text-accent font-bold mb-2">Agility</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">Reduced delivery times through efficient stakeholder management and workflow integration.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="p-8 bg-surface-elevated rounded-2xl border border-border my-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-display text-text mb-4">Competencies Applied</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="badge">Stakeholder Management</span>
          <span class="badge">Product Strategy (MVP)</span>
          <span class="badge">Legacy Systems Integration</span>
          <span class="badge">UX Design</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* CTA */}
      <div class="mt-16 text-center">
        <a href="/#projects" class="btn-accent text-lg px-8 py-4">
          <span>See Other Projects</span>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
